node_2.subject: Isabella Rodriguez
node_2.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, open Hobbs Cafe at 8:00 am and work at the counter until 10:00 am, attend a meeting with her suppliers at 11:00 am, have lunch at 12:30 pm, spend the afternoon organizing and decorating for the Valentine's Day party at 2:00 pm, continue working at the counter until 8:00 pm, have dinner at 8:30 pm.
